{"tid":1060009,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"FTIsland崔鍾訓三年前曾酒駕，拜託警察「關照」得以隱瞞大眾！","createTime":"2019-03-13T13:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T14:05:02.000Z","uid":137470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"497d6df1cc39d9dc268b8b162a84137c0f4dc35e","tid":1060009,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:09:47.000Z","msg":"根據YTN的獨家報導，FTIsland崔鍾訓牽扯在勝利和鄭俊英的聊天室事件中。<br />\n<br />\n2016年3月，崔鍾訓因為酒駕而被首爾龍山警察局所屬的警察檢舉。 雖然不確定是暫停使用駕照，還是吊銷駕照，但當時血液酒精濃度超過0.05%的標準，<span style=\"color: red;\">崔鍾訓向負責的警察拜託不要告知大眾，酒駕的事實至今也沒有被報導過。</span><br />\n<br />\n並且崔鍾訓之後向該警察送上生日祝福簡訊，維持著親密關係。 其他藝人酒駕就要度過一段中斷演藝活動並自省的時間，而崔鍾訓三年來沒有任何問題地延續演藝活動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">崔鍾訓在勝利、鄭俊英等人所在的聊天室炫耀警察給他的「關照」。除此之外，其他警察高層向他們提供便利的事情目前也正被大眾所知。</span><br />\n<br />\n而崔鍾訓所屬公司FNC在12日發表官方立場表示藝人與此次聊天室事件無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F114801&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrXPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=438a38ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/114801</a>"},{"pid":"13cba46f2901918b62e35d9eec64ff6edcb94f7f","tid":1060009,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"並且崔鍾訓之後向該警察送上生日祝福簡訊，維持著親密關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393fc109faf62cc7ed3c1c32eba8d7e438790989","tid":1060009,"uid":135313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"呢班泡狗重唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da91d40a769af89c79fcbebb8e32c99293a3478","tid":1060009,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"估唔到佢都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi